overview.en: BTV (blockchain trust of victors) aims to solve the absolute pain points of large volatility and high risk of blockchain digital assets to the greatest extent, so that most participants can enjoy basic protection while enjoying steady income.
overview.zh: BTV托底信托胜利者通证(blockchain trust of victors)旨在最大限度地解决区块链数字资产波动大、风险高的绝对痛点，让大多数参与者获得基本保障的同时，享受稳健收益。
